Title: Insink Erator M Series 56 waste disposal with air switch
Description: Helping to make after-dinner clean up easier, the InSinkErator M Series Model 56 food waste disposal unit is designed for installation in small to medium households producing a moderate volume of food waste. This powerful disposal unit works at the touch of a button, grinding food waste, including bread crusts, vegetable peelings and even small bones into miniscule particles that can be flushed away with water, helping to minimise unpleasant lingering smells and doing away with the need for a food scraps bin.
